Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.35,0:02:11.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}[...道別之日.]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.81,0:02:15.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.15,0:02:18.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼邊睡邊笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.73,0:02:22.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒?我笑了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.31,0:02:25.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一臉無比幸福的微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.62,0:02:27.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是做了很美的夢嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.29,0:02:29.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.20,0:02:31.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很久以前...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.61,0:02:34.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.53,0:02:37.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.57,0:02:38.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.71,0:02:46.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然是非常幸福的夢可是...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.79,0:02:51.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是關於你想去的地方的夢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.37,0:03:30.24,XXX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}(閉園通知  擅自作此決定非常抱歉，本保育園已經決定閉園。在此深表歉意。另，如有需要聯絡之事宜，請聯繫園長沖浦清花。     艾草保育園  沖浦清花)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.60,0:03:56.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.90,0:03:59.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 小鳩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.87,0:04:02.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天要收拾哪裡呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.04,0:04:08.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.93,0:04:10.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.46,0:04:19.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很辛苦吧 有這麼多被子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.36,0:04:21.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係 我會一直努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.39,0:04:26.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 舊的不去新的不來嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.63,0:04:30.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舊的不去 嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.82,0:04:38.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捆好的東西就搬到玄關去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.91,0:04:39.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.13,0:04:49.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把這裡弄完了就去喝茶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.46,0:04:50.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.80,0:04:54.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,籐本君不在還真是累人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.25,0:04:59.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忙著工作嘛 籐本先生他
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.14,0:05:05.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝惠顧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.34,0:05:15.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡的工作 不用勉強加太多哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.55,0:05:17.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 請讓我做
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.00,0:05:20.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經沒有拚命掙錢的必要了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.71,0:05:22.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果要炒我就直說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.10,0:05:25.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 不是那樣的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.49,0:05:29.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 沒法說你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.61,0:05:35.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.44,0:05:40.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,決定關閉保育園
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.41,0:05:41.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.13,0:05:45.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過啊 有一點希望你能明白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.86,0:05:49.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在我覺得這樣就挺好的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.90,0:05:53.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有後悔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.29,0:05:57.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是因為沖浦讓我這樣做才做的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.35,0:06:00.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後作出這個決定的是我自己
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.12,0:06:02.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是這麼想的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.21,0:06:06.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.83,0:06:24.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.10,0:06:28.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 能請你去保育園一趟嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.10,0:06:32.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裡...那個...還有籐本先生的行李
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.69,0:06:33.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.23,0:06:37.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全扔了都沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.47,0:06:38.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.32,0:06:39.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很忙 去不了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.66,0:07:05.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是籐本
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.47,0:07:08.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 我得晚到大概一小時
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.18,0:07:47.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.91,0:07:56.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,籐本先生?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.52,0:08:39.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要命啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.85,0:08:53.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧?聽說你今天會晚來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.14,0:08:55.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事辦完就來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.56,0:09:15.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 為什麼這麼一副鬱悶的表情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.88,0:09:19.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弄得我都鬱悶得發急啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.25,0:09:22.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.09,0:09:28.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在想什麼呢 你想做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.51,0:09:32.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.96,0:09:34.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.50,0:09:35.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.62,0:09:40.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡很痛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.39,0:09:43.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾草保育園要閉園了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.06,0:09:47.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於清花老師是件好事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.06,0:09:49.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.29,0:09:53.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是籐本啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.59,0:09:56.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.05,0:09:59.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,籐本先生嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.51,0:10:01.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊 你那反應
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.52,0:10:05.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自己沒發覺嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.78,0:10:06.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.70,0:10:11.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀咧呀咧 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.07,0:10:34.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清和君
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.28,0:10:36.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.93,0:10:38.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也要去打工嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.50,0:10:39.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.51,0:10:43.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 今天是保育園房子拆除的日子...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.15,0:10:43.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.15,0:10:49.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天休息一天也沒什麼的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.68,0:10:51.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.95,0:10:56.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鄰居也出門了 我也出門一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.16,0:10:57.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要出門嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.80,0:11:00.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 晚上回來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.27,0:11:03.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要老是那副臭臉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.88,0:11:04.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.96,0:11:08.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你也抓緊點 要遲到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.34,0:11:09.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.86,0:11:11.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玻璃全部拆掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.36,0:11:12.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再倒 再倒...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.17,0:11:14.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 STOP
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.33,0:11:17.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.26,0:11:20.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師 行李都收拾好了?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.88,0:11:23.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天一天已經搬出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.79,0:11:27.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 就抓緊開始幹活吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.50,0:11:29.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個眼神凶巴巴的傢伙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.00,0:11:31.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有工作在身
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.45,0:11:34.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛 真不討人喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.41,0:11:37.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明一直在這裡受人照顧 真是無情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.69,0:11:39.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是無情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.20,0:11:44.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,籐本先生 真的很忙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.28,0:11:51.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊 不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.93,0:11:56.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是受沖浦先生所托 讓我仔細周到點
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.88,0:11:59.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他說最近來不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.22,0:12:01.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 我已經聽說了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.13,0:12:04.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像上面有很多事情要處理
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.15,0:12:08.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像我們這樣的小嘍囉當然不知道內情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.87,0:12:11.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說來 沖浦先生...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.47,0:12:14.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用擔心 一定會順利解決的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.59,0:12:16.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是沖浦先生嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.45,0:12:17.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.86,0:12:19.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清花老師
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.93,0:12:21.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.34,0:12:22.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.80,0:12:23.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.24,0:12:26.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個...因為今天就要說再見了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.18,0:12:28.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以來看看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.54,0:12:31.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經和媽媽說好了才來的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.45,0:12:32.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.60,0:12:33.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你們
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.45,0:12:36.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頭兒 可以開始了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.74,0:12:40.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師 可以開始了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.38,0:12:56.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.93,0:13:00.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 很危險大家都退得遠一點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.03,0:13:02.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是~
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.92,0:13:04.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.24,0:13:34.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.89,0:13:45.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再說一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.88,0:13:48.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這事沒什麼可商量的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.87,0:13:53.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斷了這個念頭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.06,0:13:58.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 玄琥大人太狡猾了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.72,0:14:00.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然不等我就吃點心了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.38,0:14:02.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.98,0:14:05.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑞祥 安靜點
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.64,0:14:06.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.61,0:14:08.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊?誒?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.98,0:14:14.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒?居然想抓住兔子先生?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.23,0:14:16.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.31,0:14:19.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把兔子先生作為人質和那傢伙交涉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.74,0:14:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的覺得神會和你做那種交易嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.29,0:14:25.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總比什麼都不做強啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.87,0:14:29.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我們現在這狀態都算在一起的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.34,0:14:31.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是說改就能改的契約
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.63,0:14:33.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,銀生說的沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.63,0:14:36.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不像你說的話那麼沒分寸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.69,0:14:41.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情的輕重而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.71,0:14:43.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情完了想它怎樣它就怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.29,0:14:45.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我適可而止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.27,0:14:48.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那時候沒有學到一點教訓嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.59,0:14:49.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 兩位
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.35,0:14:53.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒吃夠苦頭嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.30,0:14:57.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道會傷害到誰的話 我來告訴你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.30,0:15:02.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.16,0:15:03.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.60,0:15:07.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 算了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.17,0:15:12.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神想要你學習的 也許就是等待
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.68,0:15:16.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 那確實是我不擅長的領域
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.78,0:15:17.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.01,0:15:21.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了啊 我什麼都不會做的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.59,0:16:06.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫五百祗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.87,0:16:10.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今後會和你在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.09,0:16:26.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.17,0:16:30.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收拾完了就不能再進去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.48,0:16:32.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.27,0:16:36.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師你們保重 再見
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.27,0:16:48.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來還以為這裡挺大的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.61,0:16:50.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣子看上去...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.92,0:16:52.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.36,0:17:04.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳩 有件事想要拜託你 可以嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.12,0:17:07.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒?好的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.96,0:17:11.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你幫幫籐本君吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.79,0:17:12.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.96,0:17:18.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾草保育院可能一直都在束縛著籐本君
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.13,0:17:20.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是這樣想的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.03,0:17:24.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,束縛著是指...什麼呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.08,0:17:30.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓籐本君作為努力的籐本君生活著
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.34,0:17:36.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也一直依賴著籐本君
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.40,0:17:41.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是能早點察覺到就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.25,0:17:47.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你 籐本君
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.98,0:17:51.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清和老師
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.47,0:17:52.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彈風琴給我們聽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.03,0:18:09.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了自己 去做自己喜歡的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.74,0:18:11.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我早就該這樣對他說的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.31,0:18:15.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪有 籐本先生是真的...很努力地...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.42,0:18:19.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 正因為這樣才更是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.73,0:18:23.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是因為籐本君太過努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.63,0:18:26.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以啊 小鳩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.34,0:18:31.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,籐本君就拜託你了 陪在他身邊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.82,0:18:33.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清花老師才是...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.26,0:18:39.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是我的角色了 已經不是了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.61,0:18:50.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.18,0:18:52.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.51,0:18:54.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.94,0:18:56.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳩 不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.66,0:18:58.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.28,0:19:08.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,堂元 你...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.60,0:19:13.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是遵守約定沒有聯繫保育園的人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.88,0:19:15.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不過對管理人小姐說了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.93,0:19:16.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.02,0:19:21.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉啊小鳩 他說不想讓你們擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.51,0:19:23.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他也是不願麻煩你們...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.02,0:19:49.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個...手...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.90,0:19:57.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太 太好了呢 只是一點輕傷
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.98,0:20:01.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要太勉強了哦 大家都會擔心你的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.71,0:20:08.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一隻手不能用的話很不方便吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.61,0:20:11.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼事我能幫忙的話儘管告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.75,0:20:21.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一開始在艾草保育園那遇到你的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.38,0:20:24.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我應該說過吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.43,0:20:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要抱有什麼同情和好奇心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.33,0:20:36.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你覺得我很可憐的話 請你省省吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.06,0:20:37.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是這樣子的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.88,0:20:39.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很煩人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.06,0:20:47.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的...籐本先...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.04,0:20:59.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.53,0:21:31.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是...給我的嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.58,0:21:38.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.83,0:21:42.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是讓你在下次滿月之前收集好金平糖啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.93,0:21:43.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否則的話...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.43,0:21:47.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就會按照契約決定你的未來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.01,0:21:51.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兔子先生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.18,0:21:56.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎麼樣才能延長那個期限啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.71,0:22:02.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來會怎麼樣?你認為該怎麼做?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.39,0:22:04.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道呢 要看那傢伙自己了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.25,0:22:08.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是確實地感受到自己的責任了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.81,0:22:10.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有那場戰鬥的話
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.90,0:22:12.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子就...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.56,0:22:19.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會被殃及 出那種事了...嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.65,0:22:22.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要是我能做到的話什麼都會去做
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.33,0:22:25.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 在四季再輪迴一次以前...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.75,0:22:27.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 一季也好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.47,0:22:30.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.30,0:22:42.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.34,0:22:43.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂

Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.40,0:24:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}[...小鳩的願望.]

Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.21,0:23:11.81,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an8}なくしたものと あつめたものの狭間に
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.21,0:23:11.81,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}所失與所得的縫隙中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.42,0:23:20.26,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an8}あなたの笑顔　落ちていたの
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.42,0:23:20.26,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}遺落著你的笑顏
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.65,0:23:26.04,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an8}届きそうで　届かない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.65,0:23:26.04,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}彷彿伸手可及卻又遙不可及
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.23,0:23:31.99,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an8}飛んでゆけるわけじゃないし
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.23,0:23:31.99,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}飛又飛不起來
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.15,0:23:38.19,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an8}笑わせてあげたいだけなのに
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.15,0:23:38.19,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}我只是想讓你有更多笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.43,0:23:43.55,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an8}役立たずのこの翼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.43,0:23:43.55,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}這沒用的雙翼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.88,0:23:49.32,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an8}何のためにあるのだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.88,0:23:49.32,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}到底為什麼存在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.09,0:23:55.73,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an8}あなたの傍で笑うよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.09,0:23:55.73,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}我會在你身邊微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.01,0:24:00.57,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an8}私に出来ること
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.01,0:24:00.57,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}這是我能做到的事
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.06,0:24:07.41,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an8}暖めるだけでもいいのかな
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.06,0:24:07.41,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}哪怕給你一絲溫暖也好
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.66,0:24:12.03,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an8}せめて包みたい
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.66,0:24:12.03,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}至少想包容著你
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.49,0:24:19.35,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an8}気付くの　そのための翼と
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.49,0:24:19.35,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}終於發覺 雙翼是為此存在
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.55,0:24:27.89,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an8}今こそわたし　笑うよ
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.55,0:24:27.89,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}所以我現在 在微笑
